65
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:41,140
Ya.

66
00:04:53,380 --> 00:04:54,590
Anak muda, jangan keras kepala.

67
00:04:55,590 --> 00:04:57,230
Simu punya urusan berat akhir-akhir ini

68
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:59,230
